DDeessccrriippttiioonn
       The  function  enables  a mode in which carriage return is
       translated to newline on input.  The function disables the
       above  translation.   Initially,  the above translation is
       enabled.

RReettuurrnn vvaalluuee
       Upon successful completion,  these  functions  return  OK.
       Otherwise, they return ERR.

EErrrroorrss
       No errors are defined.

UUssaaggee
       The  default  translation  adapts the terminal to environ-
       ments in which newline is the line termination  character.
       However, by disabling the translation with the application
       can sense the pressing of the carriage return key.

